{"tid":1937074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"重有良心嘅白警麻煩你哋入一入嚟","createTime":"2020-03-21T16:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T16:38:11.000Z","uid":220787,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bd430c85c8aaac9ee74d555a5eb11e3281ce180f","tid":1937074,"uid":220787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:10:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無白警啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n根本成個警隊都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讀唔成書咪去做警察囉大家都心照不宣入面個啲係咩人黎架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: purple;\">弱智on9去考都做到狗架</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n睇下你要唔要埋沒良心去搵個兩皮幾架姐<br />\n根本班狗就係社會最低層既垃圾<br />\n比政府回收train半年咪識汪汪咁吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">今時今日<br />\n重做緊狗嘅人全部都係垃圾</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">良心？<br />\n你哋無架！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vauxLk1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvauxLk1.jpg&h=7fa9a116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇吓班狗<br />\n對住藍屍鄉黑就搭哂膊頭<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721呢<br />\n掉轉頭走啊垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n呢三萬隻狗係唔會有良心架<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警死全家！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8e91da50f96f8b4427bca038c4005523d5c5511a","tid":1937074,"uid":242050,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:11:02.000Z","msg":"本身想屌你呢個世界無白警"},{"pid":"f33f58916fbfa746bb7ea3104f4950974e39df92","tid":1937074,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e91da50f96f8b4427bca038c4005523d5c5511a","tid":1937074,"uid":242050,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:11:02.000Z","msg":"本身想屌你呢個世界無白警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:12:40.000Z","msg":"me too"},{"pid":"e7deabd9bb39e5d71bd384985117b41883687b37","tid":1937074,"uid":220787,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8e91da50f96f8b4427bca038c4005523d5c5511a","tid":1937074,"uid":242050,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:11:02.000Z","msg":"本身想屌你呢個世界無白警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"三萬隻狗都要落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e88c21dc2104ea066acf7b36958349b142939e5","tid":1937074,"uid":50998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"標題黨正確示範"},{"pid":"f2e53293f4b7da3917427b002a932620a95de8ae","tid":1937074,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:19:42.000Z","msg":"白警? 都市傳說 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6638b486439452b964ae45fd5429d1012235abb6","tid":1937074,"uid":220787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e88c21dc2104ea066acf7b36958349b142939e5","tid":1937074,"uid":50998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"標題黨正確示範"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T16:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face